title: Mid/JG OPEN- Serious R5's (Diamond+ pref)
body:
Planning to start a serious team for S6, also looking to play in the preseason aswell. The team is currently G1 after placements and we are looking to hit Diamond+ ASAP. Currently only mid and jungle are open!

Must be:
-Able to use Discord/Skype + with mic
-Available to play fairly regularly, mostly at nights after around 6pm AEST
-Over 16
-Pref. D5+

Don't mind who you are as long as you have a positive attitude and are willing to take the games somewhat seriously/are dedicated enough to stick with us for more than a few games. Add me on league (IGN- Yeou) if you're interested please message me or fill out a form from here http://goo.gl/forms/5HQEezcIyV
